description:
ReSharper Ultimate is a license that combines all individual JetBrains .NET tools, as well as ReSharper C++. 
Each ReSharper Ultimate license allows a single developer to use ReSharper, ReSharper C++, dotCover, dotTrace and dotMemory.
    
This package is used as a dependency by other Chocolatey packages. To install ReSharper or related tools, see the individual packages:

- [dotUltimate](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/dotUltimate/)
- [ReSharper](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/resharper)
- [ReSharper C++](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/ReSharperCpp)
- [dotCover](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/dotCover)
- [dotMemory](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/dotMemory)
- [dotPeek](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/dotPeek)
- [dotTrace](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/dotTrace)
- [TeamCity Addin](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/teamCityAddin)
- [ReSharper Ultimate All](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/resharper-ultimate-all) - Installs all the .NET tools from ReSharper Ultimate (faster than installing individual packages)
author: JetBrains
